    "title": "The AI Boom Is Here, But Who Actually Owns It?",
    "preview_text": "Artificial intelligence is no longer a niche trend, it’s becoming one of the most significant economic shifts of our time.\nAccording to recent data, 59% of investors now hold AI-related stocks, with",
    "cover_url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HFSlPD-bUAASgxV.jpg",
    "content_state": {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "rk6o",
          "text": "Artificial intelligence is no longer a niche trend, it’s becoming one of the most significant economic shifts of our time.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 43,
              "offset": 26,
              "style": "Bold"
            },
            {
              "length": 16,
              "offset": 181,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "dimds",
          "text": "According to recent data, 59% of investors now hold AI-related stocks, with ownership even higher among younger generations. At the same time, Big Tech is doubling down, committing $600–700 billion toward AI infrastructure, particularly data centers.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 20,
              "offset": 91,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "97i4a",
          "text": "The returns are already staggering. Companies like Nvidia have seen stock prices rise over 1,190% in five years, highlighting just how valuable this new wave of technology is becoming.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4bect",
          "text": "Naturally, investors want exposure.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2p9es",
          "text": "But there’s a deeper question that often goes unasked:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 35,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "dsqp7",
          "text": "Who actually owns the future of AI?",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 22,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "b5015",
          "text": "Investment ≠ Ownership",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4ouvf",
          "text": "Today, people can invest in some AI companies on the stock market.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 25,
              "offset": 22,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "3h7td",
          "text": "But almost no one can own the models themselves.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "c372e",
          "text": "And that distinction matters.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "ev8np",
          "text": "Because while capital is flowing into AI from the top down, something else is happening from the bottom up:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 94,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "510ro",
          "text": "Millions of people are already contributing to these systems every day without even realising.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 33,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "6128r",
          "text": "The Invisible Workforce Behind AI",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "215sb",
          "text": "AI isn’t just built by engineers.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2hiub",
          "text": "It’s shaped by everyday human behavior.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "dij15",
          "text": "Every search.\nEvery workflow.\nEvery interaction online.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "casud",
          "text": "These signals are used to train and refine AI models.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 38,
              "offset": 57,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "7dgfd",
          "text": "In other words, people aren’t just users of AI, they are active contributors to its development. ",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 43,
              "offset": 31,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "1lk1f",
          "text": "Yet despite this, they receive no ownership, no upside, and no recognition for the value they help create.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 28,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "6hsgg",
          "text": "The Gap, and the Opportunity",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4ffnc",
          "text": "This creates a fundamental imbalance.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "rmva",
          "text": "On one side:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9jtml",
          "text": "Investors gain exposure",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "8nuqt",
          "text": "Companies capture value",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "5v3j4",
          "text": "On the other:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "a7nrh",
          "text": "Users contribute data",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "73sok",
          "text": "Workers train the systems",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "e2kjm",
          "text": "Society powers the entire ecosystem",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 30,
              "offset": 4,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "2k78h",
          "text": "But ownership remains concentrated.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "84lq0",
          "text": "That’s the gap.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 28,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "cudci",
          "text": "A New Model for AI Ownership",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "f0t9e",
          "text": "If AI is going to become the backbone of the global economy, then the model needs to evolve.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "euuj",
          "text": "The people who help build these systems should have a stake in them.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 0,
              "length": 13,
              "offset": 23
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "1l3ml",
          "text": "That’s the idea behind Action Model.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4falt",
          "text": "A system where:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "55aps",
          "text": "Contribution is recognized",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4mdqf",
          "text": "Participation is rewarded",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "c3bls",
          "text": "Ownership is distributed",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2tipb",
          "text": "Because this isn’t just another investment trend.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "k5em",
          "text": "It’s a shift in how value is created, and who gets to benefit from it.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 18,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "dduqu",
          "text": "The Bigger Picture",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "f6197",
          "text": "AI may be the most transformative technology of this century, but its true impact won’t just be defined by what it can do.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 11,
              "offset": 22,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "52cl",
          "text": "It will be defined by who owns it.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "dfgp6",
          "text": "And whether that ownership remains concentrated…",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2coqt",
          "text": "Or becomes something everyone can be part of.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "urls": [
              {
                "fromIndex": 86,
                "text": "train.actionmodel.com/sign-up",
                "toIndex": 115
              }
            ]
          },
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "ks5k",
          "text": "Join our movement, get rewarded for training and let's own the future of AI together: train.actionmodel.com/sign-up ",
          "type": "unstyled"
        }
